Packages
Package
Description
es.codeurjc
This is the main package of the project which contains the Application class that runs the Spring Boot Application.
es.codeurjc.entities
This subpackage contains Java classes used in the web application, such as: User - All about user info and data.
es.codeurjc.controllers
This subpackage contains all Controllers used in the web application, such as: AuthController - Controls the mapping of auth page which contains all the requests related to log in and register.
es.codeurjc.controllers.rest
This subpackage contains all REST Controllers used in the web application, such as: ForgotPasswordRestController - Controls the mapping of forgot page which contains all the requests related to forgot and recovery the password.
es.codeurjc.exceptions
This package contains all related about custom exceptions created to control the curse of the App execution such as: UserNotFoundException - Exception thrown when a User is not found in database UnsupportedExportException - Exception thrown when it is impossible to export the Shoes database to a JSON Array
es.codeurjc.services
This subpackage contains all Services used in the web application, such as: UserService - Service that manage all about authenticate and serves the process of login and register of someone inside the Web Application SecurityService - Service that manage all about security ForgotService - Service that manage all mapping about forgotPassword CartService - Service that manage all mapping about CartService specially used in cart functions like add and show
